---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="COVID-19 Testing in Dallas–Fort Worth — Walk In Today | AymanCare"
  description="Same-day COVID-19 testing at four Dallas–Fort Worth locations. Walk in or book online — results explained by a provider."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Services\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"COVID-19 Testing\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/covid-19-testing/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><a href="/services/">Services</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>COVID-19 Testing</span>
  </div>

  <div class="svc-hero">
    <div>
      <span class="svc-hero-badge fade-in"><span class="ic"></span>Walk-ins welcome</span>
      <h1 class="page-title fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">COVID-19<br><em>testing.</em></h1>
      <p class="svc-hero-lede fade-in">Rapid antigen and PCR testing available at all four AymanCare locations. Walk in or book ahead — results delivered quickly, with clinical follow-up if needed.</p>
      <div class="svc-hero-chips fade-in"><span class="pill">Walk-ins welcome</span><span class="pill pill-accent">Rapid results</span><span class="pill pill-outline">Insurance accepted</span></div>
      <div class="svc-hero-ctas fade-in">
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book a test →</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-hero-visual fade-in">
      <img src="/images/stethoscope.jpg" alt="COVID-19 Testing at AymanCare">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <aside class="svc-aside">
      <div class="aside-card fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Testing details</div>
        <h3>What to <em>expect</em></h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Rapid antigen test (15–20 min)</li>
          <li>PCR molecular test (lab processed)</li>
          <li>Nasal swab collection on-site</li>
          <li>Same-visit treatment if positive</li>
          <li>Travel & employer documentation</li>
          <li>Clinical follow-up & guidance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card dark fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Need a test today?</div>
        <h3>Walk in — no <em>appointment</em> needed.</h3>
        <a href="/contact/" class="big-num">View all locations →</a>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">All four locations offer same-day testing. Call ahead or just walk in.</p>
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-accent" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Book online →</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="svc-content">
      <h2>Two tests. <em>One</em> team.</h2>
      <p>We offer both rapid antigen and PCR molecular testing for COVID-19 at all four AymanCare locations. Whether you need a quick answer for peace of mind or a lab-verified result for travel or work, we have you covered — with results you can trust and a team that explains what they mean.</p>

      <h2>Rapid <em>antigen</em> testing.</h2>
      <p>Our rapid antigen test delivers results in 15–20 minutes using a simple nasal swab. It's ideal for symptomatic patients who need quick confirmation, families checking before gatherings, and employees screening before returning to work. If the result is positive, we can begin treatment guidance during the same visit.</p>

      <blockquote>"A fast result matters most when it changes what you do next. That's why we pair every positive rapid test with a same-visit care plan."</blockquote>

      <h2><em>PCR</em> molecular testing.</h2>
      <p>For situations that require gold-standard accuracy — international travel, employer mandates, surgical clearance — we offer PCR testing processed through a certified lab. Results are typically available within 24–48 hours, and we provide the documentation format most airlines and employers require.</p>

      <h2>Positive result? <em>We're here.</em></h2>
      <p>A positive test doesn't have to mean navigating the next steps alone. Our physicians provide same-visit guidance on isolation protocols, antiviral medications like Paxlovid when clinically appropriate, symptom management, and monitoring plans — especially for patients who are older, immunocompromised, or pregnant.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-grid-band">
  <div class="svc-grid-band-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ At a glance</span>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">By the <em>numbers.</em></h2>
    <div class="three-col">
      <div class="mini-card fade-in">
        <div class="num">< 20min</div>
        <h4>Rapid test results</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="mini-card fade-in">
        <div class="num">4</div>
        <h4>Locations offering testing</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="mini-card fade-in">
        <div class="num">Same-day</div>
        <h4>Treatment if positive</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <section class="related-services">
    <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none;">
      <div>
        <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ Related services</span>
        <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">Explore <em>more</em>.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="related-grid">
      <a href="/services/walk-in-urgent-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
        <h4><em>Walk-In</em> Urgent</h4>
        <p>Same-day care for acute illness, injury, and COVID testing.</p>
        <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/services/flu-treatment/" class="related-card fade-in">
        <h4><em>Flu</em> Symptoms</h4>
        <p>Rapid flu diagnosis and treatment.</p>
        <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/services/primary-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
        <h4><em>Primary</em> Care</h4>
        <p>Long-term care and annual wellness — your family physician.</p>
        <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</section>

<section class="big-cta">
  <div class="big-cta-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Need a test today?</span>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Walk in, or<br>book <em>online.</em></h2>
    <p class="fade-in">All four AymanCare locations offer same-day COVID-19 testing. No appointment required — but you can book ahead if you prefer.</p>
    <div class="cta-row fade-in">
      <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book appointment →</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
